title: Ep. - 504 - REAL HOUSEWIVES: ULTIMATE GIRLS TRIP 2 BRIAN MOYLAN
description:
Author Brian Moylan joins Kate to review Real Housewives: Ultimate Girls Trip season 2 on Peacock TV. 

 

Kate reviews several shows including The First Class on Netflix, which follows the lives of wealthy friends who work in fashion in Barcelona, Spain.
